metadata.name: Bully Meow / IamJudasJudas Eulerbeats Genesis LP10 REMIX Collab Full Length Animated Music Video
metadata.description:
This is a hand-animated music video NFT! And there is only ONE! 

Hand-drawn by NFT artist IamJudasJudas. The full-length animation and this NFT are accompanied by a REMIX of the Eulerbeats Genesis LP 10 token produced by Bully Meow.

The Eulerbeats Genesis LP 10 token is owned by DCInvestor (@IamDCInvestor), we'd like to thank him for allowing this remix! Also a big thanks to the Eulerbeats founders, employees, and community!
